main event: Report of two contrails of unknown nationality observed at Pepperrell AFB, Newfoundland
interesting points: The observation was made via ground-based radar
The sighting lasted for 1 minute and 15 seconds
The report was filed as part of Project Blue Book, the U.S. Air Force's official UFO investigation program
The report indicates the contrails were of 'unknown nationality', suggesting they may have been associated with an unidentified aircraft
The report concludes the sighting was either a balloon or an aircraft, but the evaluation is listed as 'Explanation Unknown'
